<ab facs="#facs_398_r2l20">daſſelb vvir alſo gern tun <expan>vvölle<ex>n</ex></expan> / <expan>vvan<ex>n</ex></expan> wir vvır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_398_r2l21"><expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> freuntſchaft </del>
